===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Skyla (Masters)}}
Skyla forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|Skyla|Swanna}}, {{p|Togekiss}}, {{form|Forces of Nature|Therian Forme}} {{p|Tornadus}}, {{p|Unfezant}}, and {{p|Jumpluff}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Skyla became a playable sync pair since the game's release, with her joining the {{player}} after completing the fifth chapter of the [[PML arc]].

In this game, Skyla is one of the PML Leaders of the [[Pokémon Masters League]], handing out the {{badge|Freedom}} to those who defeat her. She has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the PML arc.
